        <main class="main">
            

<div class="hero is-dark   " data-component="Hero" style="background-image: url('/-/media/current-topics/des8801_website-transformation-project_images_education-and-skills.jpg'); " >
    <div class="hero__inner u-inner">
        <div class="hero__text">
            <!--
Please Note: This partial view is applied in the components listed below. Any modifications will be reflected in all of these components.
- Blog Grant (BlogPostPage.cshtml)
- Project Page (ProjectPage.cshtml)

